+ What's This?

This is A Problematic Theme by [[*user winkwonkboi]], designed for articles in [[[the-appliance-war-hub|The Appliance War]]] --canon-- series or within the general setting of Site-37.

On any wiki, just apply the following code at the top of the page:

[[div class="code"]]
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:black-highlighter-theme]]@@
@@[[include :scp-wiki:theme:a-problematic-theme version=1]]@@
[[/div]]

//Note: As this is a Black Highlighter based theme, the Black Highlighter theme should be used in addition for this theme to work. To learn more, go [[[theme:black-highlighter-theme|here.]]]//

----

[[=]]
In addition, there are three variants of this theme:
